# Floorplan + Obstacle Detection Integration — Walkthrough

## What Was Done

Two independently finished subsystems are now **fully integrated** into the single AidGPT application:

1. **Obstacle Detection** (always active, unchanged) — `EnhancedObstacleDetector`, `DFPN`, `ObstacleRiskEngine`  
2. **Floorplan Parsing / Agentic-RAG** (new, on-demand) — 5-agent pipeline run in background thread, panel shown beside the camera feed

