## How the Two Systems Talk to Each Other

Every 5-second inference cycle, [_on_inference_complete](file:///c:/Tim/AIDGPT/AidGPT/main.py#498-556) checks if a floorplan result is available. If yes, the **current nav step text** is prepended to `last_navigation_text`:

```
[Floorplan] Turn left. Walk 3 steps forward. You should feel the hallway opening. Turn right at the door frame.
```

This combined string is:
- Shown in the **Navigation Panel** (press `N`)  
- Spoken by the **TTS engine** automatically

The obstacle system continues to provide real-time danger alerts independently on top of this.
